Additional Notes for Civic Technology Projects:

This project is developed as part of CivicTechWR (Civic Technology Waterloo Region),
a community organization dedicated to strengthening civic engagement through
technology in the Waterloo Region of Ontario, Canada.

While this software is released under the MIT License, we encourage users to:

1. Acknowledge the civic purpose and community origin of this project
2. Consider how modifications or derivatives can serve civic and community goals
3. Share improvements back with the civic technology community
4. Respect privacy and accessibility standards when deploying or modifying
5. Engage with affected communities when implementing civic technology solutions

For questions about civic tech applications of this software, contact:
CivicTechWR community at [contact information]

